* Henry Alan Leeke (1879–1915), British track and field athlete and Olympian, son of Henry Leeke

Henry Leeke (6 February 1846Derbyshire, England, Church of England Baptisms, 1813-1916 – 21 February 1922) was a notable British amateur athlete, and one-time Amateur Champion of England in the hammer throw and shot put.
